sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant A as AI agent
  participant G as Casper GW
  participant F as CSPR.cloud facilitator
  participant C as Casper chain
  participant U as Upstream MCP/API

  A->>G: tools/call + casper_ API key
  G->>G: verify key scope + funded balance
  Note over G: rejected key never settles (401/402/403)
  G->>F: verify(x402 payment, signed by gateway signer)
  F-->>G: valid
  G->>F: settle
  F->>C: WCSPR transfer — gateway signer → provider payTo
  C-->>F: real deploy hash
  F-->>G: settled
  G->>U: execute the tool (paid)
  U-->>G: result
  G-->>A: result + x402 payment-response + receipt id
  Note over G,C: Receipt = gateway context · x402 verify/settle · Casper proof
